    ns1:previousCourses "El plan de estudios Master Universitario En Ingenieria Mecanica no tiene definidos otros requisitos para esta asignatura."@es ;
    ns1:previousKnowledge """Links and references will be provided in the course that complement its contents. Students are responsible for going through the material that might find necessary to complete their background.
The syllabus of the Master does not define pre-requisites for this course. However, it is assumed that the students has enough background in linear algebra, vector calculus, ordinary and partial differential equations, as well as programming."""@es .

